Dear <%= @visit.visitors.first.first_name %>, 
<% case @confirmation.outcome %>
<% when 'no_slot_available' %>
We’re sorry but the dates and times you chose to visit <%= @visit.prisoner.first_name %> <%= @visit.prisoner.last_initial %> at <%= @visit.prisoner.prison_name %> were not available. 
Please visit http://gov.uk/prison-visits/ to choose some alternative dates.
<% when 'not_on_contact_list' %>
You have tried to book a visit but not all visitors are on the prisoner’s contact list. You need to contact the prisoner to be added to the contact list.
<% else %>
<% raise 'bad reason' %>
<% end %>

<%= @message_from_prison_staff %>

If you have any questions, visit the prison website (<%= Rails.configuration.prison_data[@visit.prisoner.prison_name][:web] %>) or call the 
prison on <%= Rails.configuration.prison_data[@visit.prisoner.prison_name]['phone'] %>.


